data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this 2-bedroom, 2-bath home located in a vibrant 55+ community in Boynton Beach, Florida. With a 2017 roof and a 4-year-old AC, this residence offers worry-free living. The 2022 vinyl floor remodel adds a touch of modernity to the space.Enjoy the luxury of a master bedroom with a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom. Full accordion shutters provide storm protection, and the property is pet-friendly. A Florida room beckons relaxation, while the community offers outstanding amenities, including 3 clubhouses, an 18-hole golf course, pool, shuffleboard court, pool tables, and a carpentry shop.Security patrols ensure safety, and the property is available for immediate rental. Embrace the active 55+ lifestyle in Boynton Beach
